{"tid":1419893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯拜訪荃灣二坡坊福建人","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:30.000Z","uid":274607,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd7a9c143971ad4f1f7df23a5f63fe4531080b9","tid":1419893,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=1963248170446791&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1963248170446791%26_rdr&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=a5c2ed1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=1963248170446791&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n5 月既片<br />\n但今次同元朗圍村人果次好似<br />\n又係用假消息嚇 D 本身不問世事既族群「保家圍族」<br />\n正仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfd4f3b2deac9c6e4c66ddc4232044262f76d20","tid":1419893,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"何君堯再次勾結黑社會！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"24f3853723d65580155a1ebd92ec61aa419aaf01","tid":1419893,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"316ef872f1fd0a1aa07ec4b1220f39c09b00a8dc","tid":1419893,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a075967c821375fed647e21a5191c61b49ecbe6","tid":1419893,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"e1dab41c21d02c968c2e4a55d8524423ef041ad4","tid":1419893,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"561b2b87f66a62ae911d8ce379b012b1e9ed396a","tid":1419893,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣嗰班阻住同藍衫開拖既左膠們 你地依家開心啦:</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1418913/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1418913/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔撚洗屈我分化狗<br />\n<br />\n我就係企最前同藍衫對峙其中一位<br />\n明明遇藍衫之前講到明<br />\n勇武既先好行前 立定野一定打硬<br />\n<br />\n一遇藍衫 本身都準備打<br />\n就有兩個死廢物衝最前伸大雙手叫人唔好打<br />\n趕走佢地就算<br />\n然後一少部分人又和應<br />\n最後趕狗趕到力生廣場後少少就叫大家唔好追<br />\n準備轉場<br />\n<br />\n我最記得有個垃圾主動講<br />\n我地唔可以主動出手 只可以還拖<br />\n<br />\n行去地鐵站途中 後面就比人偷雞<br />\n跑返去已經見到first aid圍住<br />\n藍衫又走曬<br />\n行到死搵曬成個荃灣都冇影<br />\n<br />\n就係你班道德撚累到位手足爆頭<br />\n佔個道德高地 換黎自己友犠牲 屌你老母<br />\n你地醒未呀<br />\n<br />\n我真係想知你地咩心態<br />\n你地知道有手足比人爆頭嗰刻 <br />\n自己會唔會罪惡感<br />\n位手足既傷完全就係你地既偽善罪證<br />\n<br />\n我最後要同所有道德撚講<br />\n我唔會再犯下同樣錯誤<br />\n下次再有道德撚衝出黎阻自己人<br />\n我會撲低你地 唔會再比你地害自己友<br />\n等其他人實踐真正勇武 保護自己人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣黑社會追打義士同記者，再被反攻全紀錄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/520Y9G4ao-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F520Y9G4ao-A&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=92a51621\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/520Y9G4ao-A</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事緣片段一開頭白衣暴徒扮路人經過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/videos/478644136246276?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSaluteToHKPolice%2Fvideos%2F478644136246276%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=b56961cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/videos/478644136246276?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一相收佢地皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/B2oxDMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2oxDMC.png&h=4a7cbaec&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}